---
---
<section class="page-container section-spacer">
  <div class="geo-divider">
    <span class="geo-circle" style="background: var(--color-geo-teal);"></span>
    <span class="geo-circle" style="background: var(--color-geo-coral);"></span>
    <span class="geo-circle" style="background: var(--color-geo-amber);"></span>
  </div>
  <p class="eyebrow fade-in">interface</p>
  <h2 class="fade-in-up delay-1" style="max-width: 500px; margin-bottom: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 6rem);">Designed for clarity.</h2>
  <div class="grid-1-1" style="gap: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);">
    <div class="fade-in-up delay-2">
      <div style="background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
        <img src="/screenshots/today@2x.png" alt="Today" style="width: 100%; height: auto; display: block;" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <h4 style="font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">Today</h4>
      <p class="body-small">Timeline, tasks, habits, events, all visible at a glance.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="fade-in-up delay-3">
      <div style="background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
        <img src="/screenshots/calendar@2x.png" alt="Calendar" style="width: 100%; height: auto; display: block;" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <h4 style="font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">Calendar</h4>
      <p class="body-small">Month view with habit events and color-coded categories.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="fade-in-up delay-4">
      <div style="background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
        <img src="/screenshots/chat@2x.png" alt="AI assistant" style="width: 100%; height: auto; display: block;" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <h4 style="font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">AI assistant</h4>
      <p class="body-small">Streaming responses with visible tool calls and confirmation.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="fade-in-up delay-5">
      <div style="background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
        <img src="/screenshots/insights@2x.png" alt="Insights" style="width: 100%; height: auto; display: block;" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <h4 style="font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">Insights</h4>
      <p class="body-small">Mood trends, correlations, heatmaps, weekly reflection.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="fade-in-up delay-6">
      <div style="background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
        <img src="/screenshots/notes@2x.png" alt="Notes" style="width: 100%; height: auto; display: block;" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <h4 style="font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">Notes</h4>
      <p class="body-small">Two-pane layout with searchable sidebar and full-text editor.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="fade-in-up delay-7">
      <div style="background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
        <img src="/screenshots/settings@2x.png" alt="Settings" style="width: 100%; height: auto; display: block;" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <h4 style="font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">Settings</h4>
      <p class="body-small">LLM provider, Telegram pairing, notifications, data export.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="fade-in-up delay-8 grid-span-half">
      <div style="background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
        <img src="/screenshots/budget@2x.png" alt="Budget" style="width: 100%; height: auto; display: block;" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <h4 style="font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">Budget</h4>
      <p class="body-small">Track spending, categorize it, and see trends over time.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
